tests.cpp does not contain any test cases for this, so you’ll have to implement them yourself. My solution has 1 TEST_CASE with 3 SECTIONS: copying a 0-element List, copying a 1-element List, and copying a \(&gt;1\)-element list. The name of the TEST_CASE must be copy constructor:
